<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>NFL Playoff Teams</h1>
    <p class="lead">Playoff teams and player rosters, following the 2015 season.</p>
    <p><a href="http://petermcintyre.com/bti420/notes/feb03/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">More info &raquo;</a></p>
